      <item>
        <titleType>Short Title(s) as Introduced</titleType>
        <titleTypeCode>101</titleTypeCode>
        <title>Justice for Hind Rajab Act</title>
        <updateDate>2026-03-26T04:58:22Z</updateDate>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
        <billTextVersionCode>IH</billTextVersionCode>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <titleTypeCode>6</titleTypeCode>
        <title>To call for accountability for the killing of innocent civilians, including 5-year-old Hind Rajab and 2 paramedics, in an attack in Gaza City on January 29, 2024, by Israel Defense Forces, to require the Secretary of State to report to Congress on the attack and to determine if any of the weapons and munitions used in the attack were provided by the United States or if any of the soldiers responsible for such killings were United States citizens or were trained by the United States, and for other purposes.</title>
        <updateDate>2026-03-26T04:48:28Z</updateDate>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
        <billTextVersionCode>IH</billTextVersionCode>
      </item>
